dc_title_s: Buchanan County, Iowa, 1970, aerial photomosaic index
dc_description_s: Title supplied by cataloger based on information from sheet labels. Images are photoreductions of mosaics created from original aerial photographs. Designating symbol FS. Form of individual image numbering: FS-2LL-[number], FS-3LL-[number], FS-4LL-[number], FS-6LL-[number], or FS-7LL-[number]. Year Flown 1970. Flown by Park Aerial Surveys, Inc. Louisville, K.Y.
